record.title: REMOVAL OF NAME OF MEMBER AS COSPONSOR OF H.R. 661
record.narrative:
REMOVAL OF NAME OF MEMBER AS COSPONSOR OF H.R. 661 -- (House of Representatives - September 24, 2007)

[Page: H10736]

speaking.paragraph: Mr. Speaker, I ask unanimous consent to have my name removed as a cosponsor of H.R. 661, to which I was mistakenly added.

record.chair: Is there objection to the request of the gentleman from Nebraska?
